<div class="flex-container">
  <div>1</div>
  <div>2</div>
  <div>3</div>  
</div>

</body>
</html>


The baseline value aligns the flex items such as their baselines aligns:


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
.flex-container {
  display: flex;
  height: 200px;
  align-items: baseline;
  background-color: DodgerBlue;
}

.flex-container > div {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  width: 100px;
  margin: 10px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 75px;
  font-size: 30px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
